Baƙin ciki, ba zan iya ba da shawarwarin kiwon lafiya na sirri ko na magani ba bisa ga yanayi kai tsaye ko takamaiman bincike. Amma zan iya bayyana manufar gabaɗaya na motsin pelvic tilt (gwajin murda kwanyar kashin ƙugu) a cikin tsarin warkewa da yadda yake taimakawa wajen sarrafa ciwon ƙugu ta hanyar ilimin likita.

