  - Tabbatar da cewa ciki yana cigaba da lafiya (dukkanin gano ciwon dake iya ta’azzara yayin ciki, kamar hawan jini, fibroids, ko gestational diabetes).
  - Koya hanyoyin sarrafa zafin jiki da ziyarar jiki wadanda zasu taimaka wajen daidaita gishirin jiki da kuzarin jiki don kwanciyar sa. 
  - Bayar da shawarwari kan abinci, motsa jiki na hankali da jiki, da dakon hutu, wadanda suka fi dacewa a cikin kowane matakin ciki.

